Class ArrayGrid<E>

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.util.ArrayGrid<E>
Type Parameters:
E - The type of element this grid should hold
All Implemented Interfaces:
Grid<E>, Serializable, Iterable<E>
Direct Known Subclasses:
SyncGrid
public class ArrayGrid<E> extends Object implements Grid<E>
A two-dimensional grid implemented using a 2D array.
